    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers linear torque through eight individual throttle bodies and is mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The drivetrain remains tight, with the M Variable Differential Lock providing superb corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-engineered balance, utilizing aluminum subframes and a multi-link rear suspension that exhibits no bushing deflection. Recent service includes a full diagnostic of the VANOS system and an inspection of the throttle actuators to ensure peak operational efficiency. The braking system features ventilated, cross-drilled rotors with excellent thermal dissipation. While the car shows honest signs of enthusiast use, its mechanical trajectory is excellent, making it a prime candidate for a dedicated driver.",
